/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKtmzNb.png&h=77288fff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f484d971b3d62db1c6a23d53abdaa3f6b634485","tid":2094443,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"共同社：中共計劃以「觀察員」的名義 派出200至300名武警「常駐」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094472</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff89502dfd8124334061444f8c6fa183d251651f","tid":2094443,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/120745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F120745&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=5e7e3c19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/120745</a><br />\n<br />\n公安部表示，全力支持配合駐港國家安全公署各項工作，全力指導支持香港警隊止暴制亂、恢復秩序，全力防範、制止和懲治極少數人危害國家安全的違法犯罪行為和活動。公安部召開黨委擴大會議，由部長趙克志主持召開會議。會議指出，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">制定實施《港區國安法》是一國兩制實踐中，具有里程碑意義的一件大事，是香港回歸以來中央處理香港事務的重大舉措，對於全面準確貫徹一國兩制方針和《基本法》等，</span>具有重大現實意義和深遠歷史意義</span>。會議指出，<span style=\"color: gold;\">要認真學習貫徹《港區國安法》，全力保障法律平穩落地、有效實施，切實保障香港居民合法權益，堅決維護國家安全和香港長治久安，確保一國兩制事業行穩致遠</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-04 23:01:28</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仆街記者喺度呃字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b84a4385dfdf8a49c898f6719b43741840ee5e2","tid":2094443,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"舊聞"},{"pid":"6221279e451dbeccab02ea89f75f4d650bace8af","tid":2094443,"uid":120757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"最少搵2萬蚊一個月既popo要聽個最盡1萬蚊一個月既公安同志黎點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9476df912df4a5604c6209f43087de3efaea49","tid":2094443,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo